this kind of stuff.

36:30.605 --> 36:34.143
All I want you to do is just,
you know, sign your name.

36:35.235 --> 36:37.601
I can't.

36:37.737 --> 36:39.819
See, I...

36:42.701 --> 36:46.819
This is like evil knievel
or somebody like that.

36:46.955 --> 36:50.664
It's got nothing to do
with what we're doing.

36:50.792 --> 36:53.283
Do you understand me?
I can't. I'm sorry.

36:55.255 --> 36:57.337
I'm really sorry.

37:00.719 --> 37:05.383
Come here, my man. How about
the autograph of the next king?

37:05.515 --> 37:07.722
You can be the first.

37:11.312 --> 37:13.143
Oh, wow!

37:14.190 --> 37:16.021
Oh, wow!

37:20.488 --> 37:22.341
There, now you have something
to hang on my Lance.

37:22.365 --> 37:25.323
She's got plenty
to hang on your Lance.

37:27.704 --> 37:30.741
- I owe you, grundy.
- Hey, retail prices, you know.

37:30.874 --> 37:32.865
Thanks, man.

38:00.028 --> 38:03.486
Very clever, very clever.
But he's a comedian.

38:06.451 --> 38:10.160
- Speaking of clowns...
- Yeah, he's still here.

38:10.288 --> 38:12.404
- What do you think?
- I don't know.

38:32.435 --> 38:35.097
- What now?
- Let's go raise some hell!

38:35.230 --> 38:36.595
All right!

39:12.058 --> 39:13.514
Damn, he's good.

39:34.831 --> 39:37.664
Hey! I'm really impressed!

39:38.585 --> 39:41.122
