39:41.254 --> 39:44.792
- All you had to do was ask.
- Thanks.

39:44.924 --> 39:47.165
- By the way...
- Yeah?

39:47.302 --> 39:49.133
Look out for that barn!

39:49.262 --> 39:50.422
