- Compromise.

42:00.101 --> 42:03.389
Change doesn't have
to mean compromise.

42:03.521 --> 42:05.603
We're bigger now. Things are different.

42:05.732 --> 42:08.474
Christ, we've got an overhead!

42:12.363 --> 42:15.355
Publicity helps the overhead.

42:15.491 --> 42:18.198
They're bringing in more crowds.

42:18.327 --> 42:19.908
More sucker-headed
American driftwood

42:20.038 --> 42:23.030
that can't tell the difference
between me and Jim Jones

42:23.166 --> 42:26.408
or Charles manson
or the great wallenda.

42:26.544 --> 42:30.082
That kid... that kid thinks
