42:48.983 --> 42:52.066
j you is always lyin' and signifyin'

42:52.195 --> 42:54.937
j but you better not monkey with me j

42:58.826 --> 43:01.909
- all right!
- Nice! Finel

43:02.038 --> 43:03.403
all right!

43:11.089 --> 43:14.707
I was never into
this king Arthur crap anyway.

43:14.842 --> 43:19.757
I was into the bikes, man, the bikes.
That's how I got here.

43:19.889 --> 43:22.221
He just recently found out
Morgan le fay was a woman.

43:25.728 --> 43:28.970
That's all right.
Pip's known all his life he's a woman.

43:29.148 --> 43:31.434
Oh...!

43:38.574 --> 43:40.986
Are you gay, pip?

43:41.119 --> 43:44.987
In the sense of happy,
carefree, light-hearted?

43:45.123 --> 43:47.159
