44:31.711 --> 44:34.418
I don't, ok?

44:35.756 --> 44:38.122
Well, maybe that's why
you take so much heat, huh?

44:40.595 --> 44:42.506
I mean, rocky doesn't take any heat.

44:42.638 --> 44:46.347
- Yeah, that's cos rocky kicks ass.
- No, that's not true.

44:46.475 --> 44:49.933
I don't take any heat
because I know who I am,

44:50.062 --> 44:52.724
and very often I do kick ass.

45:17.840 --> 45:20.582
J down a country Lane
I strolled on a door, I chanced to knock

45:20.718 --> 45:24.552
j have you any pots and kettles
with a rusty hole...

45:27.391 --> 45:31.475
- Did you invite company?
- No, just you, I guess.

45:33.731 --> 45:35.096
Oh, man.

45:35.233 --> 45:37.940
Oh, Jesus. Oh, Jesus, it's the swine.

45:38.069 --> 45:41.311
- I smell bacon.
- That's the swine, man.

45:41.447 --> 45:44.189
Oh, whither goest, thou yonder?

45:56.128 --> 45:59.040
Come on.

46:00.716 --> 46:04.004
- Hello!
- Open up!

46:04.136 --> 46:05.592
What's going on?

46:05.721 --> 46:08.963
