Bagman ain't going to no jail alone.

48:22.525 --> 48:24.982
We got a show
to do in three days!

48:25.111 --> 48:28.649
- We do have to get there.
- Maybe we can't make it.

48:28.781 --> 48:31.221
Oh, yeah, sure, sure. We haven't
got enough problems as it is.

48:31.283 --> 48:33.865
I do think you boys ought to reconsider.

48:33.994 --> 48:37.407
Small town jails is,
er... uncomfortable places.

48:37.540 --> 48:39.747
Damn uncomfortable.

48:39.875 --> 48:42.708
All them lead pipes and stuff.

48:42.837 --> 48:45.374
Bagman ain't going to no jail alone.

48:46.507 --> 48:50.341
Anything happens in that jail,
there's gonna be a witness.

48:52.638 --> 48:55.926
The rest of you stay here
until we get out.

49:01.522 --> 49:05.106
Now are you going
to arrest me, fat man,

49:05.234 --> 49:07.771
or do I have to do something
to provoke you?

49:07.903 --> 49:10.315
All right, Jack, you got it.

49:24.545 --> 49:26.410
Aw, Christ.

49:27.798 --> 49:29.754
Let's go.

49:29.884 --> 49:33.297
That man's hurt. Better not be worser
when I see him again.

49:33.429 --> 49:35.044
Neither one of 'em. You hear me?

49:35.181 --> 49:39.015
Oh, that's right, you're a doctor.
Damn lucky thing you're around, doc.

49:39.143 --> 49:40.143
Hit it.

49:40.269 --> 49:42.260
Wait here.

49:45.524 --> 49:46.524
This is crazy!

49:46.650 --> 49:49.210
Let's go after them, pay them,
and then get the hell out of here!

49:49.278 --> 49:51.189
We're not paying!
That's the way Billy wants it!

49:51.322 --> 49:52.437
Billy's insane!

49:52.573 --> 49:54.693
It's done, Morgan!
There's nothing we can do about it.

49:54.783 --> 49:56.193
Oh, that's great.

49:56.327 --> 49:59.444
So, what, we save 500 bucks here and
we lose 2,000 for blowing a show?

49:59.580 --> 50:00.580
That's good.

50:00.706 --> 50:05.291
We're not gonna lose anything.
We're going to Lawrence.

50:05.419 --> 50:08.377
Angie, you go ahead now
with tuck and pip.

50:08.506 --> 50:09.506
When you get to a phone,

50:09.632 --> 50:12.339
try all the motels in Lawrence
and see if you can find Steve.

50:12.468 --> 50:16.006
If you can't raise him by phone, as
soon as you get to town, try to find him.

50:16.138 --> 50:18.492
The rest of us, we got some packing
to do. We're moving out.

50:18.516 --> 50:20.427
I need somebody
to drive bagman's truck.

50:20.559 --> 50:22.095
I want to be on the road in an hour.

50:22.228 --> 50:23.348
Let's get organised.

50:23.395 --> 50:25.886
We got to load up all the bikes.
Who's gonna drive what.

50:26.023 --> 50:28.376
Bobbie, come help me with the tents.
We're gonna strike them right now.

50:28.400 --> 50:29.981
- All right.
- Let's go.

50:30.110 --> 50:32.066
I'll drive the truck.

50:36.742 --> 50:39.859
You better stay,
see what you can do.

50:39.995 --> 50:41.155
I got some ideas.

50:41.747 --> 50:44.079
No! Nol

50:44.208 --> 50:45.618
nol

50:45.751 --> 50:48.288
- you wanted a witness? Huh?
