50:51.131 --> 50:54.919
All you gotta do is tell me to send out
for your boys with the money!

50:55.052 --> 50:56.883
That's what you gotta do!

50:57.012 --> 50:59.879
Don't hit him no more.

51:00.015 --> 51:02.176
Ok?

51:07.481 --> 51:10.063
- Bagman.
- What?

51:10.192 --> 51:13.400
- You ok, man?
- I'm all right.

51:23.664 --> 51:25.700
Sheriff's up in loyal gorge,
