51:45.352 --> 51:47.468
Er... we just needed to see
the sheriff, that's all.

51:47.605 --> 51:49.015
- Sorry to bother you.
- Yeah.

51:49.148 --> 51:53.232
Julie Dean! You don't just come
around banging on people's doors

51:53.360 --> 51:55.271
at four o'clock in the morning!

51:55.404 --> 51:57.924
What the hell you doing up
